info.description: Apache Ranger is a framework to enable, monitor and manage comprehensive data security across the Hadoop platform. Apache Ranger currently provides a centralized security adminstration, fine grain access control and detailed auditing for user access within Apache Hadoop, Apache Hive, Apache HBase and other Apache components
